n大家都有少少唔捨得"},{"pid":"0baae5cda8afe3f7a6a747f89fb2b47f36aeb27b","tid":657970,"uid":108022,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T21:56:04.000Z","msg":"同同事做朋友仍兵家大忌，一涉及有利益關係就好易變質<br />\n有好多途徑識新朋友既姐"},{"pid":"fcbcebc4344d6f83ca0e280a6811a6efc89a807f","tid":657970,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:54:29.000Z","msg":"試過，仲喊埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以為以後見唔到<br />\n點知過左1星期返返去做pt<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16d08df893e7d3e4c759a2a8b27b7b57ecbdb79","tid":657970,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0baae5cda8afe3f7a6a747f89fb2b47f36aeb27b","tid":657970,"uid":108022,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T21:56:04.000Z","msg":"同同事做朋友仍兵家大忌，一涉及有利益關係就好易變質<br />\n有好多途徑識新朋友既姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"但我覺得同事都可以好深感情 <br />\n一旦克服左利益關係既障礙 感情真係可以好深 亦都係好難得"},{"pid":"f8b2a2fd320cd977a369f8b06f9f7c13dcf12666","tid":657970,"uid":170320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e16d08df893e7d3e4c759a2a8b27b7b57ecbdb79","tid":657970,"uid":9136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0baae5cda8afe3f7a6a747f89fb2b47f36aeb27b","tid":657970,"uid":108022,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T21:56:04.000Z","msg":"同同事做朋友仍兵家大忌，一涉及有利益關係就好易變質<br />\n有好多途徑識新朋友既姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:00:09.000Z","msg":"但我覺得同事都可以好深感情 <br />\n一旦克服左利益關係既障礙 感情真係可以好深 亦都係好難得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:09:05.000Z","msg":"可能你份工無咩利益衝突姐，由同事做到朋友真係唔容易。<br />\n你平時無咩朋友？我都無咩朋友，出左泥做野朋友係會少左。我都想識新朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25fd2258824b81635218648648577d394f9c522","tid":657970,"uid":171594,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:10:12.000Z","msg":"大部份同事只係過客，唔使太上心<br />\n真係有緣既，離職後都可以保持聯絡既<br /